rComments: I second BEST Professor EVER.  PERIOD.

This was such a fun course! The assignments are challenging but they are well thought out and give you good exposure to a lot of different kinds of mapping. Prof Mui is kind and gives interesting lectures. There are also lots of opportunities for extra credit if you're motivated. You need the textbook too to study for tests.

Fantastic professor that works really hard to engage students. You will need the textbook because some of the things she tests on are not in the lectures. Her assignments are laid out very clearly and she is very approachable when you have questions. This course might be a little tough if you are new to statistics terminology.

Prof Amy is one of the best profs I've ever had! She's such a nice and sweet person, very approachable and friendly with her students. She gives chances for extra credit, extends deadlines, and makes really easy tests. Her step-by-step approach for explaining concepts is very easy to follow! Overall, she's an amazing prof and I will take her again!
